content: [2025 | Age 22] [TextBlock(text="Just left the serene world of Japan, where the fusion of tradition and tech painted a picture of what urban life could be. Now, stepping into the electric pulse of NYC, I wonder: can we maintain that harmony as we scale? Here's to finding out, and shaping the future with both eyes open.", type='text')]

[2025 | Age 22] [TextBlock(text="As I turn 22, I'm struck by how quickly life's pace has accelerated. My journey with blockchain and AI coding assistants feels like a microcosm of the world's technological race. Yet, amidst the code and the buzz, it's the quiet moments with family, reflecting on our shared stories, that ground me. Here's to a year of balancing the digital with the deeply human.", type='text')]
